# Installing {{ project_title }}

There are several ways to install {{ project_name }}.
We strongly recommend using a virtual environment to avoid conflicts with
other packages and projects on your system.

## Quick Start

Choose your preferred installation method:

1. [**Pixi** (recommended for development)](#installing-with-pixi-recommended) - Reproducible environments with exact dependency versions
2. [**pip**](#installing-with-pip) - Standard Python package installation
